articles.description: Nana Foulland had 21 points and nine rebounds, Zach Thomas added 15 points and Bucknell held off Holy Cross 68-67 on Saturday as neither team made a field goal in overtime.
articles.headline: Bucknell hits 20-win mark for the 14th time

articles.description: Duke has figured out how to cope without one of its most productive players, and now it's Clemson's turn to do the same.
articles.headline: Stars' status in limbo as No. 12 Duke visits No. 11 Clemson
